org.apache.commons.collections4.keyvalue

Class DefaultMapEntry<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.commons.collections4.keyvalue.AbstractKeyValue<K,V>
      • org.apache.commons.collections4.keyvalue.AbstractMapEntry<K,V>
        • org.apache.commons.collections4.keyvalue.DefaultMapEntry<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - the type of keys
    V - the type of mapped values
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Map.Entry<K,V>, KeyValue<K,V>

    public final class DefaultMapEntry<K,V>
extends AbstractMapEntry<K,V>
    A restricted implementation of Map.Entry that prevents the Map.Entry contract from being broken.

    3.0
